name: Kahlua® Fruit Dip
author: luv2cook
summary: This light dip goes quickly at parties. Be prepared with the recipe! It goes well with apples, bananas, strawberries, grapes, but not so much with melon-type fruits. It also makes a great pie filling in an Oreo® crust!
ingredients: 1 (8 ounce) container frozen whipped topping, thawed
1 (3 ounce) package instant vanilla pudding mix
½ cup coffee-flavored liqueur (such as Kahlua®)
directions: Mix whipped topping, pudding mix, milk, and coffee-flavored liqueur together in a bowl
Refrigerate dip until set, 1 hour to overnight
